 OCC: wow way to ignore the flare blasts jp.
  Galvatron saw Hell beats start to retreat. He was only a few feet from him 
now. He jumped opff a rock and attempted to wrap his hands around his neck 
and pull him to the ground. His laser hands shot off 2 feet wide blasts as he 
did so. Quiledart  shot  a bomb charge in the way of thier retreat route 10 
yards ahead of them. The bomb hit the ground creating a 20 foot bunker. It 
would slow them down. Megatron turned into tank mode and shot of plasma 
blasts at the retreating enemy.

--part1_a8.1171bc8a.27c5a7f3_boundary
